                    <h1>Adecco Group launches 2016 ‘CEO for One Month’ initiative in India for the first time</h1>
                </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
	<div class="spanContainer-3" id="PL1-Container8">
		<div class="span-3" id="PL1-Container9">
